name             unrtf
version          0.20.5
categories       textproc
maintainers      nomaintainer
description      RTF converter
long_description \
	UnRTF is a command-line program written in C which \
	converts documents in Rich Text (.rtf) format to HTML, \
	LaTeX, PostScript, plain text and other formats.
